4.3.11
Waste Management
This section describes the DOE waste generation baseline that will be used to gauge the relative impact of MPF construction and operations on the overall waste generation at NTS and on DOE's capability to manage such waste.
NTS manages the following types of waste: TRU waste, including mixed TRU waste; LLW; mixed LLW; hazardous waste; and sanitary waste.
Table 4.3.11Â­1 provides the routine waste generation rates at NTS.
